title: Meet The Press - 2008-06-22 - Brian Williams Sitting In
description:
TV Show: Meet The Press with Tim Russert (Brian Williams Sitting In)
Episode: Decision 2008, Campaign Financing
Air Date: Sunday, June 22, 2008
Network: NBC

Exclusive! NBC&#039;s Brian Williams moderates a Decision 2008 debate: For the Obama campaign ? Sen. Joe Biden (D-DE). For the McCain campaign ? Sen. Lindsey Graham (R-SC). Graham and Biden square off on Iraq, the economy and rising gas prices. Plus, a political roundtable with John Harwood and Andrea Mitchell.

Guests:
- Sen. Joe Biden (D-DE), Obama supporter
- Sen. Lindsey Graham (R-SC), National Co-Chair, McCain Campaign
- John Harwood, New York Times; Chief Washington Correspondent, CNBC
- Andrea Mitchell, Chief Foreign Affairs Correspondent, NBC News
